1. Example for if else (Even, Odd numbers)
How to write a script for Even odd number

#!/bin/bash
echo "Enter a Number: "
read num

if (( num % 2 == 0 ))
then 
     echo "Number is Even"
else 
     echo "number is Odd"
fi

